import React from 'react'
import HomeLeft from '../home/home_left/HomeLeft'
import VideoFollow_right from './VideoFollowRight'
export default function VideoFollow() {
    return ( <
        div className = "row"
        style = {
            { paddingTop: '20px' } } >
        <
        HomeLeft > < /HomeLeft> <
        VideoFollow_right / >
        <
        /div>
    )
}
